data.description: Avast, mateys! Feast yer eyes on this remarkable treasure, a real estate gem fit for a savvy pirate like yourself. Behold the property at 2365 W Bayshore Dr., where adventure and luxury blend harmoniously. Situated along captivating Carancahua Bay, it offers breathtaking sunrise views. Multiple shaded decks, hurricane-rated shutters, and hardi siding ensure durability. From exterior to interior, discover spacious living areas with tropical-inspired custom paint. The kitchen features a large storage island, pantry & tile counters for elegant culinary escapades. The primary suite has a cavernous layout, patio access, and a walk-in closet for yer treasures. Downstairs, there is a screened patio and guest suite complete with bath, storage & workshop. Fenced yard, vegetable garden, and mature shade trees provide privacy and cover for secret meetings. Additional parking for yer seaworthy vessel & RV. Don't miss this chance to own a slice of pirate paradise in Palacios, Texas.
